flowchart LR
    input["用户输入<br/>场景 / PID / NPU 映射 / 优化目标"]
    linux[Linux 目标节点]
    collector[只读采集器]
    snapshot[Host CPU Snapshot JSON]
    rules[诊断规则 R001-R010]
    plan["Affinity Plan<br/>保守方案 / 进阶方案 / 回滚命令"]
    html[自包含 HTML 报告]
    apply["确认后执行<br/>taskset 或 internal-script"]
    rollback["rollback-state.json<br/>原始 affinity / PID starttime"]
    verify[Before / After 验证]

    input --> collector
    linux --> collector
    collector --> snapshot
    snapshot --> rules
    rules --> plan
    snapshot --> html
    plan --> html
    plan --> apply
    apply --> rollback
    rollback --> verify
    html --> verify
